Revision history for Perl extension Snartemo::Tk.

0.01  Tue Sep  7 11:31:26 1999
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.18

0.5   Sep 14 1999
	- first iteration of Tk user interface

0.6
	- added ability to see twist
	- added control over background color
	- added option to make short vs long shapes (with/without overlap from
	row to row)
	- diplays file name or "untitled" in title of window
	- almost every dialog now is cached in the object with each object
	having its own instance
	- added ability to have cards idle
